This is a Loopcomm device.
"LOO0020 Rev:1.2" is silkscreened on the board.
[http://www.dd-wrt.com/phpBB2/viewtopic.php?t=77020 On the DD-WRT forums] (high-res internal pictures, OUI derived from label on back of the PCB) :[http://www.dd-wrt.com/phpBB2/viewtopic.php?t=71960 and again] (says device uses RTL8186P, which makes no sense considering this is an N-class router)
The power adapter included with the device is an ''unbranded'' YHSW-120100U (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.13A max. -> 12VDC 1000mA).
